<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ʿndy ạlrạḥh lyk yạlly tʿbạn
 ʿndy sʿạdh lyk wạ̉nt lyh ḥyrạn)2
 1-(yạʿạysẖ fy kwrh bʿydh yạ tạyh fy blạd gẖrybh)2
 tʿạly̱ wsyb ạlḥyrh lk ʿndy ạ̉frạḥ mjydh
 2-(ạ̉tdẖkr ṣlyby wdmy yạ ạbny ạ̉nạ ʿạyzk jnby)2
 tʿạl wsyb ạlʿạlm ạ̉nạ ḍạmn yạạbny slạmk
 3-(mstnyk msẖtạq lrjwʿk hnsyk tʿbk wdmwʿk)2
 tʿạl wạ̉trk ạ̉ḥzạnk ạ̉nạ ḍạmn yạ ạbny mkạnk</lyrics>
